title: Emerica and Bryan Herman Present the Herman G6 Vulc
description:
The #HermanG6 vulc is now available at your local #HigherQuality skate shop.

The #HermanG6 Vulc is infused with the Herman DNA, highlighting Emerica’s new G6 in-sole technology, available now at #HigherQuality skate shops for $64.99.
